import React from "react";


const CircleProgress = ({size, strokeWidth}) =>{
    const viewBox = `0 0 ${size} ${size}`;
    const radius = (size - strokeWidth) / 2;
 
  return (

    <svg width="262" height="262" viewBox="0 0 262 262" >
    <circle 
        cx="131" 
        cy="131" 
        r="100" 
        fill="none" 
        stroke="#e6e6e6" 
        stroke-width="20" stroke-dasharray="628.3185307179587, 628.3185307179587" 
        stroke-linecap="round" 
        classaAme="RCP__track" >
    </circle>
    <circle 
        cx="131" 
        cy="131" 
        r="100" 
        fill="#ffffff" 
        stroke="indianred" 
        stroke-width="20"

        stroke-dashoffset="213.62830044410595"

        class="RCP__progress" >

    <circle 
      cx="200" 
      cy="50%" 
      r="28" 
      fill="white" 
      stroke="indianred" 
      stroke-width="3" 
      class="RCP__pointer" >
    </circle>
    </svg>
)
}
export default CircleProgress;
